title: Mission to the Edge of Space - Red Bulratos
description:
Mission to the Edge of Space Aerial - Documentary

This anniversary documentary captivates audiences once again with unseen footage of the historic event. The tale of a nerve-racking five-year mission with tough flight tests, emotional roller coasters, missed deadlines, failing gear and serious glitches up to the last minute looks back through the eyes of Felix Baumgartner, Joe Kittinger and the team. 

123 minutes

1280x720/29fps
